<sect1 id="dir_1b0fbe5df8695f68df77faff1a12338c_1autotoc_md102">
<title>helios.engine.builder.spawnSystem</title><para>Fluent, ID-centric builder API for configuring the spawn system: pools, profiles, and schedulers.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1b0fbe5df8695f68df77faff1a12338c_1autotoc_md103">
<title>Overview</title><para><computeroutput>SpawnSystemFactory</computeroutput> provides an API where each <bold>pool ID</bold> is the entry point for all related configuration. Profiles and scheduling rules are nested under their pool, ensuring co-location of related IDs and reducing configuration errors.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1b0fbe5df8695f68df77faff1a12338c_1autotoc_md104">
