<codeline><highlight class="normal">├──<sp/>SpawnSystemFactory.ixx<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>Entry<sp/>point<sp/>(analog<sp/>to<sp/>GameObjectFactory)</highlight></codeline>
